text.section:
The immunity from civil liability for any personal injury under subsection (1) of this section includes:
A health-care practitioner who prescribes or authorizes the emergency use of the epinephrine auto-injector;
A pharmacist who fills a prescription for the epinephrine auto-injector;
A certified individual who provides or administers the epinephrine auto-injector;
An authorized entity who stores or provides the epinephrine auto-injector to a certified individual or authorized noncertified individual; and
An individual trainer or training entity providing the certified individual.
